text:
I want to draw border for header cells. I tried using 

 HSSFCellStyle headerStyle = workBook.createCellStyle();
 headerStyle.setBorderTop((short)50);

but still I'm not getting solid line. I'm new to this API. Please help me to 
get to the speed.

Do you have any documentation for HSSF component? Please send me the URL.

Use HSSFCellStyle.BORDER_* constants to set cell border:

 HSSFCellStyle headerStyle = workBook.createCellStyle();
 headerStyle.setBorderTop(HSSFCellStyle.BORDER_THIN);
 headerStyle.setRightBorderColor(HSSFColor.BLACK.index);

P.S. Next time please post usage questions in poi-user mailing list.

Yegor
